IN NO EVENT SHALL THE AUTHORS OR COPYRIGHT HOLDERS BE LIABLE FOR ANY CLAIM,  
DAMAGES, OR OTHER LIABILITY ARISING FROM THE USE OF THIS SOFTWARE.  

---

## 9. Termination

- Rights terminate automatically upon violation of this license
- Reinstatement requires explicit written approval from the Founder

---

